---
description: shadcn/ui component conventions
globs: "frontend/src/components/**/*.tsx"
alwaysApply: false
---

UI components follow shadcn/ui conventions:

- Components in `src/components/ui/` for primitives (button, card, badge, etc.)
- Application components in `src/components/screens/` and `src/components/overlays/`
- Kebab-case filenames: `diagnosis-card.tsx`, `status-bar.tsx`
- Use `cn()` utility from `@/lib/utils` for class name merging
- Radix primitives for accessible interactive components
- Import pattern: `import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"`
- Dark mode via class strategy on `<html class="dark">`
- CSS variables for theming (defined in `src/index.css`)
- No inline styles when Tailwind classes exist for the property
